      ******************************************************************
       Procedure Division                using d-seq-edi
                                               rf-oft
                                               rf-ofr                 .
      ******************************************************************

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Main program                                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       main-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione status di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   d-seq-edi-exi-sts      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test preliminare su codice fornitore            *
      *              * ___                                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-oft-cod-arc       not  = 0000001
                     go to main-999.
       main-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del tipo operazione      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura testata                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        d-seq-edi-tip-ope    =    "WT"
                     perform wrt-tes-edi-000
                                          thru wrt-tes-edi-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura riga                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   d-seq-edi-tip-ope    =    "WR"
                     perform wrt-rig-edi-000
                                          thru wrt-rig-edi-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Open                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   d-seq-edi-tip-ope    =    "OP"
                     perform rou-opn-fls-000
                                          thru rou-opn-fls-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Close                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   d-seq-edi-tip-ope    =    "CL"
                     perform rou-cls-fls-000
                                          thru rou-cls-fls-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test cancellabilita' modulo                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   d-seq-edi-tip-ope    =    "C?"
                     perform tst-cnc-mod-000
                                          thru tst-cnc-mod-999        .
       main-999.
           exit program.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Open                                                      *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       rou-opn-fls-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento contatore Open modulo                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-nol-ctr-opn          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione contatore righe                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-emi-ctr-rig          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione indice per selezione w-bin-byt   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-byt-inx-000      thru det-byt-inx-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione C0 Control Characters            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-asc-c0c-000      thru det-asc-c0c-999        .
       rou-opn-fls-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open output file [bin]                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Pathname di base files sequenziali          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PB"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "asc "               to   s-nam                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione nome archivio : AANNNNNN.TXT   *
      *                  *                                             *
      *                  * - AA     : Anno, ultime 2 cifre             *
      *                  * - NNNNNN : Numero ordine                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-oft-num-doc       to   w-emi-num-doc          .
      *
           move      spaces               to   w-fil-bin-pat-bin      .
           string    s-pat      delimited by   spaces
                     "/exp/"    delimited by   size
                     w-emi-num-doc-ann
                                delimited by   size
                     w-emi-num-doc-prg
                                delimited by   size
                     ".TXT"     delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-pat-bin      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Open                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   fil-bin-opn-000      thru fil-bin-opn-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se status ad errore : uscita            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-err                not  =  spaces
                     move  "#"            to   d-seq-edi-exi-sts
                     go to rou-opn-fls-999.
       rou-opn-fls-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Close                                                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       rou-cls-fls-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Segmento di chiusura                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Footer                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Incremento contatore righe              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-emi-ctr-rig          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lunghezza stringa                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      08                   to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Composizione e scrittura                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
           string    "C9,"      delimited by   size
                     w-emi-ctr-rig
                                delimited by   size
                     w-c0c-CR   delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Scrittura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   fil-bin-wrt-000      thru fil-bin-wrt-999        .
       rou-cls-fls-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Decremento contatore Open modulo                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           subtract  1                    from w-nol-ctr-opn          .
       rou-cls-fls-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close file [bin]                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   fil-bin-cls-000      thru fil-bin-cls-999        .
       rou-cls-fls-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Test cancellabilita' modulo                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       tst-cnc-mod-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se il contatore di Open e' a zero il modulo e'  *
      *              * cancellabile, altrimenti non lo e'              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-nol-ctr-opn        =    zero
                     move  spaces         to   d-seq-edi-exi-sts
           else      move  "#"            to   d-seq-edi-exi-sts      .
       tst-cnc-mod-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura testata                                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-tes-edi-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Segmento di apertura                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Version                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lunghezza stringa                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      05                   to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Composizione e scrittura                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
           string    "C0,1"     delimited by   size
                     w-c0c-CR   delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Incremento contatore righe              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-emi-ctr-rig          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Scrittura                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   fil-bin-wrt-000      thru fil-bin-wrt-999        .
       wrt-tes-edi-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Segmento di testata                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Separatore                             GEPC *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      ","                  to   w-emi-val-gpc-sep      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * ID                                     GEPC *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "C1"                 to   w-emi-val-gpc-rec      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Buyer number                           GEPC *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "0000000001"         to   w-emi-val-gpc-buy      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sales organisation                     GEPC *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "00001"              to   w-emi-val-gpc-sls      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ship to                                GEPC *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "0000000001"         to   w-emi-val-gpc-shp      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Order number                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-oft-num-doc       to   w-emi-num-doc          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Order date                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-oft-dat-doc       to   s-dat                  .
           move      s-saa                to   w-emi-dat-doc-yyy      .
           add       1900                 to   w-emi-dat-doc-yyy      .
           move      s-mes                to   w-emi-dat-doc-mes      .
           move      s-gio                to   w-emi-dat-doc-gio      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Delivery date                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-oft-dat-cns       to   s-dat                  .
           move      s-saa                to   w-emi-dat-cns-yyy      .
           add       1900                 to   w-emi-dat-cns-yyy      .
           move      s-mes                to   w-emi-dat-cns-mes      .
           move      s-gio                to   w-emi-dat-cns-gio      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Currency                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "EUR"                to   w-emi-sgl-vpf-sgl      .
       wrt-tes-edi-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura segmento                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lunghezza stringa                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Composizione e scrittura                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
           string    w-emi-val-gpc-rec
                                delimited by   size
                     w-emi-val-gpc-sep
                                delimited by   size
                     w-emi-val-gpc-buy
                                delimited by   size
                     w-emi-val-gpc-sep
                                delimited by   size
                     w-emi-val-gpc-sls
                                delimited by   size
                     w-emi-val-gpc-sep
                                delimited by   size
